WEBVTT

23:31.050 --> 23:32.920 line:80%
I should be thanking you, right?

23:33.350 --> 23:34.680 line:80%
That's not what I meant.

23:35.170 --> 23:36.410 line:80%
I just never expected

23:36.990 --> 23:38.220 line:80%
that for this house,

23:38.630 --> 23:40.040 line:80%
you would act so rashly

23:40.370 --> 23:42.530 line:80%
and give yourself to
a crippled refugee from Chongzhou.
